Package: spexvb
Type: Package
Title: Parameter Expanded Variational Bayes for High-Dimensional Linear Regression
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(person('Peter', 'Olejua', email = 'polejua@email.sc.edu', role = c('aut', 'cre'), comment = c(ORCID = '0000-0002-2478-0908')), person('Alexander', 'McLain', email = 'mclaina@mailbox.sc.edu', role = 'aut'))
Description: Implements a parameter expanded variational Bayes algorithm for linear regression models with high-dimensional variable selection. The methodology utilizes spike-and-slab priors to perform simultaneous estimation and selection.
